The paper focuses on enhancing the quality of compressed video using deep learning techniques, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM) categories. The paper also uses Support Vector Machine (SVM) and Convolutional Neural Network (CNN) algorithms, which are commonly used in information retrieval (cs.IR) and machine learning (cs.LG) categories.
